лд, суффолк, Англия","lifeSummary":"Arnold de Bedingfield родился около 1090 г. в местности бедингфиелд, суффолк, Англия. Его отца звали Peter de Bedingfield. Он женился на женщине по имени Christiana Orframnia в 1118 г. У них было по крайней мере 3 сына. Он умер около 1171 г. в местности бедингфиелд, суффолк, Англия, Великобритания в возрасте 83 лет и был похоронен в местности бедингфиелд, суффолк, Англия."},"sm":{"about 1090–about 1171":"e tusa o le 1090–e tusa o le 1171","1090–1171":"1090–1171","1093–Female":"1093–Ua Maliu","1120–1194":"1120–1194","1122–Male":"1122–Ua Maliu","1124–Male":"1124–Ua Maliu","1059–Male":"1059–Ua Maliu","1090":"1090","about 1171":"e tusa o le 1171","about 1090":"e tusa o le 1090","1120":"1120","1096":"1096","1194":"1194","1171":"1171","1093":"1093","1118":"1118","1106":"1106","1059":"1059","1124":"1124","Abt 1122":"e tusa o le 1122","1122":"1122","about 1124":"e tusa o le 1124","about 1120":"e tusa o le 1120","Of Bedingfield, Suffolk, England":"Bedingfield, Suffolk, Egelani, United Kingdom","Bedingfield, Suffolk, England":"Bedingfield, Suffolk, Egelani"},"sk":{"about 1090–about 1171":"okolo 1090–okolo 1171","1090–1171":"1090–1171","1093–Female":"1093–Zosnulá","1120–1194":"1120–1194","1122–Male":"1122–Zosnulý","1124–Male":"1124–Zosnulý","1059–Male":"1059–Zosnulý","1090":"1090","about 1171":"okolo 1171","about 1090":"okolo 1090","1120":"1120","1096":"1096","1194":"1194","1171":"1171","1093":"1093","1118":"1118","1106":"1106","1059":"1059","1124":"1124","Abt 1122":"okolo 1122","1122":"1122","about 1124":"okolo 1124","about 1120":"okolo 1120","Of Bedingfield, Suffolk, England":"Bedingfield, Suffolk, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Bedingfield, Suffolk, England":"Bedingfield, Suffolk, England"},"es":{"about 1090–about 1171":"aproximadamente 1090–aproximadamente 1171","1090–1171":"1090–1171","1093–Female":"1093–Fallecida","1120–1194":"1120–1194","1122–Male":"1122–Fallecido","1124–Male":"1124–Fallecido","1059–Male":"1059–Fallecido","1090":"1090